OL,3,CTyson Fury says 16-year-old daughter's
OL,4,Cwedding day was 'emotional'
OL,6,FBoxer Tyson Fury has said it was an
OL,7,F"emotional moment" seeing his 16-year-
OL,8,Fold daughter Venezuela in her wedding
OL,9,Fdress for the first time.
OL,11,FThe teenage reality star, who appears
OL,12,Fin the Netflix series 'At Home With
OL,13,FThe Furys,' tied the knot with her 19-
OL,14,Fyear-old boyfriend Noah Price on the
OL,15,FIsle of Man on 16 May.
OL,17,FIn England and Wales, you must be at
OL,18,Fleast 18 years old to marry or form a
OL,19,Fcivil partnership, and it is illegal
OL,20,Fto marry under 18, even with parental
OL,21,Fconsent.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@RO]
