OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779120673
OL,3,CTyson Fury says 16-year-old daughter's
OL,4,Cwedding day was 'emotional'
OL,6,FThe legal age for marriage in the Isle
OL,7,Fof Man is 16 with parental consent.
OL,9,FTyson Fury moved his family to the
OL,10,FIsle of Man from Morecambe in 2025
OL,11,Fbecause of the number of disturbed
OL,12,Fvisitors who would arrive at his house
OL,13,Fat all hours of the day and night.
OL,15,FWriting on Instagram, boxer Fury said:
OL,16,F"Wow seeing her in the dress for the
OL,17,Ffirst time was an emotional moment for
OL,18,Fme! and the realization that her
OL,19,Fgetting married was upon me! (sic)"
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@cO]
