OL,3,CTyson Fury says 16-year-old daughter's
OL,4,Cwedding day was 'emotional'
OL,6,FIn another clip he can be seen walking
OL,7,Fhis daughter down the aisle and said:
OL,8,F"A beautiful day of celebrating my
OL,9,Fdaughter's wedding day,
OL,10,F@venezuelaprice1 she was amazing & I'm
OL,11,Fvery proud of her! we both were crying
OL,12,Flike babys. (sic)"
OL,14,FVenezuela also posted a video on
OL,15,FTikTok of her youngest brother Prince
OL,16,FRico Paris and her boxer father seeing
OL,17,Fher in her dress ahead of the ceremony.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@RO]
