OL,3,CTyson Fury says 16-year-old daughter's
OL,4,Cwedding day was 'emotional'
OL,6,FThe clip uses audio from the 1991 film
OL,7,F'Father Of The Bride', in which Steve
OL,8,FMartin plays the father of a young
OL,9,Fwoman getting married and talks about
OL,10,Fhis sadness at saying farewell to his
OL,11,Fchild.
OL,13,FVenezuela has been sharing frequent
OL,14,Fupdates on her nuptials with her
OL,15,F985,000 followers, recently revealing
OL,16,Fher husband is wearing his wedding
OL,17,Fring on a chain round his neck, rather
OL,18,Fthan on his finger.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
