OL,3,CTyson Fury says 16-year-old daughter's
OL,4,Cwedding day was 'emotional'
OL,6,FShe posted a photo alongside her
OL,7,Ffather Tyson Fury of her wedding day,
OL,8,Fwhich she captioned: "Well I couldn't
OL,9,Fof asked for a better father all my
OL,10,Flife he has gone above and beyond for
OL,11,Fme 1 in a million (sic)."
OL,13,FShe has also revealed the couple are
OL,14,Fheading off on honeymoon, but added
OL,15,Fshe will not say where they are flying
OL,16,Fto because "I don't want to be hunted
OL,17,Fdown".
OL,26,@xD@LOUyD@EO]
