OL,3,CTyson Fury says 16-year-old daughter's
OL,4,Cwedding day was 'emotional'
OL,6,FOn the morning of her wedding, she
OL,7,Fshared a video of herself falling out
OL,8,Fof bed, lip synching to a clip from
OL,9,FFriends in which Monica, played by
OL,10,FCourteney Cox, celebrates it is her
OL,11,Fwedding day and falls over.
OL,13,FThe family's reality show 'At Home
OL,14,FWith The Furys' follows the
OL,15,Fheavyweight champion as he exits the
OL,16,Fring and tries to embrace retirement
OL,17,Fwith his family, including his wife,
OL,18,FParis, father, John, and their
OL,19,Fchildren.
